Title: Hey, Maybe One Day You’ll See Me Again
Lyrics:
Hey, Maybe One Day You’ll See Me Again Lyrics[Chorus]
Hey, maybe one day you'll see me
Hey, maybe one day you'll see me
Hey, maybe one day you'll see me
Hey, maybe one day you'll see me

But everyday, you go through my mug
